<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>UX Color Themes</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --font-sans: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
            --background: #ffffff;
            --foreground: #020817;
            --card: #ffffff;
            --card-foreground: #020817;
            --popover: #ffffff;
            --popover-foreground: #020817;
            --primary: #2563eb;
            --primary-foreground: #fafafa;
            --secondary: #f1f5f9;
            --secondary-foreground: #0f172a;
            --muted: #f1f5f9;
            --muted-foreground: #64748b;
            --accent: #f1f5f9;
            --accent-foreground: #0f172a;
            --destructive: #ef4444;
            --destructive-foreground: #fafafa;
            --border: #e2e8f0;
            --input: #e2e8f0;
            --ring: #94a3b8;
            --radius: 0.5rem;
        }

        body {
            font-family: var(--font-sans);
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            color: var(--foreground);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        h1, h2, h3 {
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: -0.025em;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.25rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
            margin-top: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        h3 {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .header-description {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 3rem auto;
            color: #64748b;
        }

        .themes-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .theme-card {
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            background-color: var(--card);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
        }
        
        .theme-card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .palette {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .swatch {
            border-radius: calc(var(--radius) - 2px);
            padding: 0.75rem;
            color: white;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        
        .swatch.light {
            color: #020817;
            text-shadow: none;
        }

        .swatch .label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        
        .swatch.primary { grid-column: 1 / 3; }
        .swatch.secondary { grid-column: 3 / 5; }
        .swatch.accent { grid-column: 1 / 5; }

        .components-preview {
            background-color: var(--background);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            white-space: nowrap;
            border-radius: calc(var(--radius) - 2px);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: var(--primary);
            color: var(--primary-foreground);
        }
        
        .btn-secondary {
            background-color: var(--secondary);
            color: var(--secondary-foreground);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        
        .btn-destructive {
            background-color: var(--destructive);
            color: var(--destructive-foreground);
        }
        
        .btn:disabled {
            opacity: 0.5;
            cursor: not-allowed;
        }

        .alert {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 1rem;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        
        .alert-success {
            background-color: #f0fdf4;
            border-color: #bbf7d0;
            color: #15803d;
        }
        
        .alert-destructive {
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            border-color: #fecaca;
            color: #b91c1c;
        }
        
        .input {
            display: flex;
            height: 2.5rem;
            width: calc(100% - 2rem);
            border-radius: calc(var(--radius) - 2px);
            border: 1px solid var(--input);
            background-color: var(--background);
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }
        
        .input:focus {
            outline: 2px solid var(--ring);
            outline-offset: 2px;
        }

        .card-preview {
            background-color: var(--card);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 1rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        
        .card-preview h4 {
            margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
            color: var(--card-foreground);
        }
        
        .card-preview p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: var(--muted-foreground);
        }
        
        /* Theme specific styles */
        #theme1-card {
            --primary: #22c55e;
            --primary-foreground: #f0fdf4;
            --secondary: #f1f5f9;
            --accent: #a3e635;
            --background: #f8fafc;
            --foreground: #020817;
            --card: #ffffff;
            --card-foreground: #020817;
            --muted-foreground: #64748b;
            --border: #e2e8f0;
            --input: #e2e8f0;
            --ring: #4ade80;
        }
        #theme2-card {
            --primary: #f97316;
            --primary-foreground: #ffffff;
            --secondary: #fed7aa;
            --accent: #fbbf24;
            --background: #fffbeb;
            --foreground: #422006;
            --card: #ffffff;
            --card-foreground: #422006;
            --muted-foreground: #7c2d12;
            --border: #fed7aa;
            --input: #fed7aa;
            --ring: #fb923c;
        }
        #theme3-card {
            --primary: #3b82f6;
            --primary-foreground: #eff6ff;
            --secondary: #e0e7ff;
            --accent: #60a5fa;
            --background: #f5f8ff;
            --foreground: #1e293b;
            --card: #ffffff;
            --card-foreground: #1e293b;
            --muted-foreground: #475569;
            --border: #dbeafe;
            --input: #dbeafe;
            --ring: #60a5fa;
        }
        #theme4-card {
            --primary: #8b5cf6;
            --primary-foreground: #f5f3ff;
            --secondary: #e9d5ff;
            --accent: #c084fc;
            --background: #faf5ff;
            --foreground: #2e1065;
            --card: #ffffff;
            --card-foreground: #2e1065;
            --muted-foreground: #581c87;
            --border: #e9d5ff;
            --input: #e9d5ff;
            --ring: #a78bfa;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Color Theme Exploration</h1>
    <p class="header-description">
        Below are four distinct theme directions for the application. Each theme includes a color palette and live component examples to help visualize the look and feel. Review each one and decide which direction best fits the "Creative and Inspired" vision of the project.
    </p>

    <div class="themes-grid">
        
        <!-- Theme 1: Fresh & Organic -->
        <div class="theme-card" id="theme1-card">
            <h2>1. Fresh & Organic</h2>
            <p style="color: var(--muted-foreground); margin-top: -1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Calm, Natural, Trustworthy. Perfect for highlighting the connection to food and sustainability.</p>
            
            <h3>Palette</h3>
            <div class="palette">
                <div class="swatch primary" style="background-color: var(--primary); color: var(--primary-foreground);">#22c55e <span class="label">Primary</span></div>
                <div class="swatch secondary light" style="background-color: var(--secondary); color: var(--secondary-foreground);">#f1f5f9 <span class="label">Secondary</span></div>
                <div class="swatch accent light" style="background-color: var(--accent); color: var(--secondary-foreground);">#a3e635 <span class="label">Accent</span></div>
            </div>

            <h3>Components</h3>
            <div class="components-preview">
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                    <button class="btn btn-primary">Save Item</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-secondary">Cancel</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-destructive">Delete</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-primary" disabled>Save Item</button>
                </div>
                <input class="input" placeholder="e.g., 'Tomatoes'">
                <div class="alert alert-success">Success! Your pantry is updated.</div>
                <div class="card-preview">
                    <h4>Expiring Soon</h4>
                    <p>3 items are expiring in the next 2 days.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Theme 2: Creative & Vibrant -->
        <div class="theme-card" id="theme2-card">
            <h2>2. Creative & Vibrant</h2>
            <p style="color: var(--muted-foreground); margin-top: -1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Energetic, Inspiring, Bold. This theme makes the app feel fun and full of possibilities.</p>
            
            <h3>Palette</h3>
            <div class="palette">
                <div class="swatch primary" style="background-color: var(--primary); color: var(--primary-foreground);">#f97316 <span class="label">Primary</span></div>
                <div class="swatch secondary light" style="background-color: var(--secondary); color: var(--foreground);">#fed7aa <span class="label">Secondary</span></div>
                <div class="swatch accent light" style="background-color: var(--accent); color: var(--foreground);">#fbbf24 <span class="label">Accent</span></div>
            </div>

            <h3>Components</h3>
            <div class="components-preview" style="background-color: var(--background);">
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                    <button class="btn btn-primary">Find a Recipe</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-secondary">I'll pass</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-destructive">Clear</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-primary" disabled>Find a Recipe</button>
                </div>
                <input class="input" placeholder="e.g., 'Chicken, Rice'">
                <div class="alert alert-success" style="background-color: #fffbeb; border-color: #fde68a; color: #b45309;">Voila! Here are 5 recipes for you.</div>
                <div class="card-preview">
                    <h4>Instant Idea</h4>
                    <p>What ingredients do you have on hand?</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Theme 3: Modern & Efficient -->
        <div class="theme-card" id="theme3-card">
            <h2>3. Modern & Efficient</h2>
            <p style="color: var(--muted-foreground); margin-top: -1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Focused, Productive, Sleek. A clean, tech-forward feel that emphasizes intelligence.</p>
            
            <h3>Palette</h3>
            <div class="palette">
                <div class="swatch primary" style="background-color: var(--primary); color: var(--primary-foreground);">#3b82f6 <span class="label">Primary</span></div>
                <div class="swatch secondary light" style="background-color: var(--secondary); color: var(--foreground);">#e0e7ff <span class="label">Secondary</span></div>
                <div class="swatch accent light" style="background-color: var(--accent); color: var(--primary-foreground);">#60a5fa <span class="label">Accent</span></div>
            </div>

            <h3>Components</h3>
            <div class="components-preview" style="background-color: var(--background)">
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                    <button class="btn btn-primary">Add to Pantry</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-secondary">Dismiss</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-destructive">Remove</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-primary" disabled>Add to Pantry</button>
                </div>
                <input class="input" placeholder="Search inventory...">
                <div class="alert alert-destructive">Warning: 2 items have expired.</div>
                <div class="card-preview">
                    <h4>Inventory Status</h4>
                    <p>You have 42 items in your pantry.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Theme 4: Warm & Welcoming -->
        <div class="theme-card" id="theme4-card">
            <h2>4. Warm & Welcoming</h2>
            <p style="color: var(--muted-foreground); margin-top: -1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Friendly, Approachable, Comforting. Evokes the feeling of a home kitchen and delicious food.</p>
            
            <h3>Palette</h3>
            <div class="palette">
                <div class="swatch primary" style="background-color: var(--primary); color: var(--primary-foreground);">#8b5cf6 <span class="label">Primary</span></div>
                <div class="swatch secondary light" style="background-color: var(--secondary); color: var(--foreground);">#e9d5ff <span class="label">Secondary</span></div>
                <div class="swatch accent light" style="background-color: var(--accent); color: var(--primary-foreground);">#c084fc <span class="label">Accent</span></div>
            </div>

            <h3>Components</h3>
            <div class="components-preview" style="background-color: var(--background)">
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                    <button class="btn btn-primary">I Cooked This!</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-secondary">Maybe Later</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-destructive">Nevermind</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-primary" disabled>I Cooked This!</button>
                </div>
                <input class="input" placeholder="Filter recipes...">
                <div class="alert alert-success" style="background-color: #f5f3ff; border-color: #ddd6fe; color: #5b21b6;">Nice! Your pantry has been updated.</div>
                <div class="card-preview">
                    <h4>Lasagna Recipe</h4>
                    <p>Ready in 60 minutes. Serves 4.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
